frus:attachment.p:
3. In developing our informational approach, the USIE should stress the mutual interests of South Asian
                        countries and the United States in the following: 
                            (a)

Maintenance of national freedom;
                            (b)

Maintenance of characteristic indigenous cultures;
                            (c)

Maintenance of peace, security, and freedom from external
                                aggression;
                            (d)

The development of social and economic progress;
                            (e)

The development of democracy.
